====芝加哥小熊====
2016年1月21日，川崎宗則和[[芝加哥小熊|芝加哥小熊]]簽署了一份帶有春訓邀請的小聯盟合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.cubs.mlb.com/news/article/162471596/cubs-sign-munenori-kawasaki-with-spring-invite|title=Cubs ink Kawasaki to Minors pact with invite|last=Muskat|first=Carrie|work=MLB.com|date=January 21, 2016|accessdate=January 21, 2016|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424021941/http://m.cubs.mlb.com/news/article/162471596/cubs-sign-munenori-kawasaki-with-spring-invite|dead-url=no}}</ref>他於3月29日被釋出，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2016/03/cubs-release-shane-victorino-manny-parra-munenori-kawasaki.html|title=Cubs Release Shane Victorino, Manny Parra, Munenori Kawasaki|last=Todd|first=Jeff|work=mlbtraderumors.com|date=March 29, 2016|accessdate=March 29, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108110607/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2016/03/cubs-release-shane-victorino-manny-parra-munenori-kawasaki.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>並於當日稍後簽署了另一份小聯盟合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/chicago-cubs-release-former-blue-jay-kawasaki/|title=Report: Cubs release, re-sign Munenori Kawasaki|last=Liddell|first=MacKenzie|work=[[Sportsnet|Sportsnet]]|date=March 29, 2016|accessdate=March 29, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108184718/https://www.sportsnet.ca/baseball/mlb/chicago-cubs-release-former-blue-jay-kawasaki/|dead-url=no}}</ref>4月3日，他被加進小熊的40人名單並派往3A球隊艾奧瓦小熊。4月8日，因{{link-en|凱爾・舒瓦伯|Kyle Schwarber}}進傷兵而進入25人名單，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.desmoinesregister.com/story/sports/baseball/iowa-cubs/2016/04/08/kawasaki-could-headed-back-chicago-cubs/82796452/ |title=Chicago Cubs recall fan-favorite Munenori Kawasaki |date=April 8, 2016 |accessdate=April 8, 2016 |first=Tommy |last=Birch |work=Des Moines Register}}</ref> 隨後因[[哈維爾·巴耶茲|哈維爾·巴耶茲]]傷癒於4月15日下放至小聯盟。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/15210841/javier-baez-chicago-cubs-activated-15-day-disabled-list |title=Cubs activate Javier Baez from DL |work=Associated Press |date=April 15, 2016 |accessdate=April 15, 2016 |archive-date=2016-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160730084722/http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/15210841/javier-baez-chicago-cubs-activated-15-day-disabled-list |dead-url=no }}</ref>他於7月9日升上大聯盟，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-cubs-option-jeimer-candelario-recall-munenori-kawasaki-20160709-story.html |title=Cubs option Jeimer Candelario, recall Munenori Kawasaki |date=July 9, 2016 |accessdate=July 9, 2016 |first=Mark |last=Gonzales |work=Chicago Tribune |archive-date=2019-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420171404/https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-cubs-option-jeimer-candelario-recall-munenori-kawasaki-20160709-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 但又於7月15日下放至3A。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/cubs-munenori-kawasaki-optioned-to-triple-a-25631707/ |title=Cubs' Munenori Kawasaki: Optioned to Triple-A |date=July 15, 2016 |accessdate=August 7, 2016 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107030600/https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/cubs-munenori-kawasaki-optioned-to-triple-a-25631707/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>9月6日，他再一次被小熊召上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://chicagocubsonline.com/archives/2016/09/cubs-reinstate-rondon-recall-almora-jr-patton-kawasaki-select-federowicz.php|title=From the Wire: Cubs Reinstate Rondon, Recall Almora Jr., Patton and Kawasaki, Select Federowicz|date=September 6, 2016|work=Chicago Cubs Online|accessdate=September 16, 2016|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119204055/https://chicagocubsonline.com/archives/2016/09/cubs-reinstate-rondon-recall-almora-jr-patton-kawasaki-select-federowicz.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在2016年賽季的14場大聯盟出賽中，他取得打擊率0.333、1分打點及2次盗壘。小熊最後以103勝58敗的成績在[[國家聯盟中區|國聯中區]]稱王，並成功贏得[[2016年世界大賽|2016年世界大賽]], 結束長達108年的冠軍荒。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bastian|first1=Jordan|last2=Muskat|first2=Carrie|title=Chicago Cubs win 2016 World Series|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207938228/chicago-cubs-win-2016-world-series/|publisher=MLB|accessdate=November 3, 2016|archive-date=2017-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130223630/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207938228/chicago-cubs-win-2016-world-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref>儘管川崎宗則並不合乎2016年季後賽的參加資格，但他仍跟著球團在季後賽移動並參與慶功活動。

2017年1月7日，川崎宗則和小熊簽了新的小聯盟合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/01/minor-mlb-transactions-1717.html|title=Minor MLB Transactions: 1/7/17|last=Wilmoth|first=Charlie|work=mlbtraderumors.com|date=January 7, 2017|accessdate=January 7, 2017|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112034854/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/01/minor-mlb-transactions-1717.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他於3月28日被球團釋出。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/03/cubs-release-munenori-kawasaki.html|title=Cubs Release Munenori Kawasaki|last=Todd|first=Jeff|work=mlbtraderumors.com|date=March 28, 2017|accessdate=March 28, 2017|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112005301/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/03/cubs-release-munenori-kawasaki.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

